                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۲‏ پاسخ صحیح است. معنی عبارت سؤال: </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">سال تحصیلی از ....... ماه تشکیل می</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">شود.</span><span class="az-text">»</span></div><div><span class="az-text">ترجمه گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها:</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۱‏) دوازده</span><span>                        </span><span class="az-text">۲‏) نُه [‏سال تحصیلی از نُه ماه (تِسعَ</span><span class="az-text">ة</span><span class="az-text"> شُهُور) تشکیل می</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">شود.]‏</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۳‏) هفت</span><span>                        </span><span class="az-text">۴‏) ده</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2347273_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> اِثنَي</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">عشر</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2347273_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> تِسعَة</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2347273_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> سَبعَة</span></div>
