                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۴‏ پاسخ صحیح است. ما أجابَ الْفَرَسُ الصَّغیرُ. </span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7218-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53333" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53334" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53335" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53336" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53337" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7218"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="az-text"> اسب کوچک جواب نداد.</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2351258_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> هُوَ یَذْهَبُ إلَی الْقَرْیَةِ</span><span class="cz-text"> الْمُجاوِرَةِ</span><span class="cz-text">. </span><span class="cz-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7214-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53313" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53314" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53315" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53316" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53317" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7214"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="cz-text"> او به روستای مجاور (همسایه) می</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">رود.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351258_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> لاَِنَّ والِدي</span><span class="cz-text"> في</span><span class="cz-text"> مُهِمَّةٍ</span><span class="cz-text"> إداریَّةٍ</span><span class="cz-text">. </span><span class="cz-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7215-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53318" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53319" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53320" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53321" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53322" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7215"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="cz-text"> برای این</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">که پدرم در مأموریت اداری هست.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351258_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> أَ أنتِ تَذهَبینَ إلی المُختَبرِ وَحدَکِ؟ </span><span class="cz-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7216-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53323" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53324" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53325" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53326" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53327" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7216"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="cz-text"> ‌آیا تو تنهایی به ‌آزمایشگاه می</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">روی؟</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351258_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> ما أجابَ الْفَرَسُ الصَّغیرٌ. </span><span class="cz-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7217-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53328" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53329" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53330" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53331" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53332" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7217"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="cz-text"> اسب کوچک جواب داد.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '4', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1027', '258', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">گزینهٔ </span><u><span class="rz-text">ناهماهنگ</span></u><span class="rz-text"> کدام است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۲‏ پاسخ صحیح است. به</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">جز گزینهٔ ۲‏ بقیهٔ گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها فعل هستند. اَعْلَمْ: داناتر، داناترین</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2351101_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> فَهِمَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351101_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> أعْلَمْ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351101_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> بَقِیَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351101_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> حَرَسَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '2', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1028', '264', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">فعل کدام گزینه با دیگر گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span class="rz-text">ها </span><u><span class="rz-text">متفاوت</span></u><span class="rz-text"> است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۳‏ پاسخ صحیح است. </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">قالَتْ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> در گزینهٔ ۳‏ فعل ماضی است</span><span><img class="unique" src="/images/Questions/15/193/256/264/e4ef5bfd-dcd3-4d72-aea3-405bba486dd5.png"></span><span class="az-text">امّا در گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">های (۱‏) </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">یَفْرَحُ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text">، (۲‏) </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">تَسْمَعُ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> و (۴‏) </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">یَلْعَبُ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text">، هر سه فعل مضارع هستند.</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2350861_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> هُوَ یَفْرَحُ لِلتَّجْرِبَةِ</span><span class="cz-text"> الْجَدیدَةِ</span><span>.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2350861_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> هی تَسْمَعُ کَلامَ اُمِّها.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2350861_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> قالَتْ أُمُّ الْفَرَسِ لِوَلَدِها.</span><span>                        </span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2350861_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> اَلْوَلَدُ یَلْعَبُ بِسَیّارَتِهِ.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '3', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:57:08');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1029', '260', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span>«</span><span class="rz-text">الْعِلْمُ ....... وَ مِفْتاحُهَا السُّؤالُ.</span><span>»</span><span class="rz-text"> عیّن الإسم المناسب للفراغ:</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۱‏ پاسخ صحیح است. </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">اَلْعِلْمُ خَزائنُ و مِفْتاحُهَا السُّؤالُ.</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> خَزائن یعنی گنجینه</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها. بررسی سایر گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها:</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۲‏) مَصابیح </span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7219-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53338" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53339" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53340" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53341" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53342" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7219"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="az-text"> چراغ</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها</span><span>                        </span><span class="az-text">۳‏) أبصار </span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7220-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53343" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53344" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53345" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53346" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53347" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7220"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="az-text"> دیدگان</span><span>                        </span><span class="az-text">۴‏) دُموع </span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7221-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53348" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53349" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53350" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53351" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53352" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7221"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="az-text"> اشک</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2349761_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> خَزائنُ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2349761_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> مَصابیحُ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2349761_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> أبصار</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2349761_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> دُموع</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '1', '40', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1030', '252', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span>«</span><span class="rz-text">نَحْنُ ....... في</span><span class="rz-text"> الْحیاةِ</span><span>.</span><span>»</span><span class="rz-text"> عیّن الفعل المضارع المناسب:</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۴‏ پاسخ صحیح است. با توجه به ضمیر </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">نَحْنُ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> در جمله، فعل </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">نَصْدُقُ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> درست است.</span></div><div><span class="az-text">نَحْنُ نَصْدُقُ ف</span><span class="az-text">ي</span><span class="az-text"> الْحیا</span><span class="az-text">ة</span><span class="az-text">: ما، در زندگی سخن راست را می</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">گوییم.</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2352424_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> أصْدُقُ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2352424_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> یَصْدُقُ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2352424_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> تَصْدُق</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2352424_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> نَصْدُقُ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '4', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1031', '259', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">در کدام گزینه رابطه، </span><u><span class="rz-text">نادرست</span></u><span class="rz-text"> است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۳‏ پاسخ صحیح است. شاهَدَ </span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7224-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;munderover&gt;&lt;mo&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;mrow /&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;&amp;#x645;&amp;#x62A;&amp;#x631;&amp;#x627;&amp;#x62F;&amp;#x641;&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/munderover&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53363" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53364" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53365" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53366" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53367" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53368" class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-itable"><span class="mjx-row"><span class="mjx-cell"><span class="mjx-stack"><span class="mjx-over" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-bottom: 0.157em; padding-top: 0.141em;"><span id="MJXc-Node-53371" class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span id="MJXc-Node-53372" class="mjx-mtext"><span class="mjx-char" style="padding-top: 0.575em; padding-bottom: 0.218em;"><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.264em; width: 0.543em;">م</span><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.264em; width: 0.871em;">ت</span><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.264em; width: 0.314em;">ر</span><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.264em; width: 0.229em;">ا</span><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.264em; width: 0.486em;">د</span><span class="mjx-charbox MJXc-TeX-unknown-R" style="padding-bottom: 0.264em; width: 0.857em;">ف</span></span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-op"><span id="MJXc-Node-53369" class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-delim-h"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.35em; margin: 0px -0.056em 0px -0.055em;">←</span><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.35em; margin: 0px 0.037em 0px -0.205em; letter-spacing: -0.311em;">−−</span><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.35em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: -0.084em;">−</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-row"><span class="mjx-under" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-top: 0.636em; padding-bottom: 0.141em; padding-left: 1.65em;"><span id="MJXc-Node-53370" class="mjx-mrow" style=""></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mrow><munderover><mo>⟵</mo><mrow></mrow><mrow><mtext>مترادف</mtext></mrow></munderover></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7224"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mrow><munderover><mo>⟵<mrow> <mrow><mtext>مترادف </script></span><span class="az-text"> رَأیَ است، به معنی: مشاهده کرد، دید.</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2349736_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> قادِم </span><span class="cz-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7222-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mo&gt;&amp;#x2260;&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53353" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53354" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53355" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53356" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53357" class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.432em; padding-bottom: 0.575em;">≠</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mo>≠</mo></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7222"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"> <mo>≠ </script></span><span class="cz-text"> ماضي</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2349736_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> بَساتین = حَدائِق</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2349736_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> شاهَدَ </span><span class="cz-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7223-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mo&gt;&amp;#x2260;&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53358" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53359" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53360" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53361" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53362" class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.432em; padding-bottom: 0.575em;">≠</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mo>≠</mo></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7223"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"> <mo>≠ </script></span><span class="cz-text"> رَأیَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2349736_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> أَتَی = جاءَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '3', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1032', '208', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">در کدام گزینه حرف </span><span>«</span><span class="rz-text">مای منفی</span><span>»</span><span class="rz-text"> به کار رفته است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۲‏ پاسخ صحیح است. بررسی گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها:</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۱‏) واژهٔ </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">بَعْدَما</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> یعنی: پس از این</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">که</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۲‏) فعل </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">ما رَأَیْتُکِ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> یعنی: تو را ندیدم (فعل منفی)</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۳‏ و ۴‏) واژهٔ </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">ما</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> یعنی: چیست؟ / چه چیزی؟ (کلمهٔ پرسشی)</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2351699_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> بَعْدَما یَسْمَحُ لي</span><span class="cz-text"> والِدي</span><span>.</span><span>                        </span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351699_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> فَکَیْفَ ما رَأَیْتُکِ حَتَّی الاْٰنَ؟</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351699_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> مَا ذلِکَ في</span><span class="cz-text"> یَدِکَ؟</span><span>                        </span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351699_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> ما مَعْنَی إسْمِکِ؟</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '2', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1033', '239', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span>«</span><span class="rz-text">أَنْتِ رَجَعْتِ قَبْلَ ساعَةٍ</span><span class="rz-text"> و أنْتَ ....... بَعْدَ ساعةٍ</span><span>.</span><span>»</span><span class="rz-text"> اِجعَل الفعل المناسب في</span><span class="rz-text"> الفراغ:</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۲‏ پاسخ صحیح است. با توجّه به واژهٔ </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">بَعْدَ ساع</span><span class="az-text">ةٍ»</span><span class="az-text"> یعنی بعد از یک ساعت، باید از فعل مستقبل استفاده شود. و </span><span class="az-text">با توجّه به ضمیر </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">أنتَ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> باید فعل مذکر استفاده شود</span><span><img class="unique" src="/images/Questions/15/193/228/238/239/5f223c85-0133-4012-9496-088b16108b94.png"></span><span class="az-text">بنابراین گزینهٔ ۲‏ </span><span class="az-text">«</span><span class="az-text">سَوْفَ تَرْجِعُ</span><span class="az-text">»</span><span class="az-text"> درست است.</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2353150_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> تَرْجِعینَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2353150_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> سَوْفَ تَرْجِعُ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2353150_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> سَوْفَ تَرْجِعینَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2353150_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> سَوْفَ رَجَعْتَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '2', '40', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:57:08');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1034', '230', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">در کدام گزینه هر دو واژه درست معنا شده است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۴‏ پاسخ صحیح است. ۱‏) خواهیم رفت / ۲‏) بالا بردم / ۳‏) به نظر تو</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2351349_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> سَنَذهَبُ: خواهم رفت - وَحدَکَ: به تنهایی تو</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351349_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> نَشرَه: انتشارش - رَفَعتُ: بالا رفتی</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351349_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> حَقیبَتُکَ: باغ تو - بِرَایکَ: برایت</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2351349_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> تَزرَعُ: می</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">کارد - وَجَع: درد</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '4', '40', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1035', '307', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">کدام گزینه از نظر ضمایر (أنتِ - أنتما - هُم - أنتنّ) هماهنگ است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۱‏ پاسخ صحیح است. ضمایر صورت سؤال با فعل</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">های گزینهٔ ۱‏ همخوانی دارد.</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2352269_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> تَفعَلینَ - سَمِعتُما - رَجَعُوا - تَرجِعنَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2352269_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> یَنصُرُ - قَذَفا - وَقَعنَ - یَسلمونَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2352269_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> نَزرعُ - رَجَعتُ - اَخرجُ - سَمِعنا</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2352269_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> دَخلتِ - تَدخلونَ - جَمعتِ - تَنصُرُینَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '1', '40', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1036', '231', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">کدام گزینه درست ترجمه شده است؟</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۱‏ پاسخ صحیح است. اصلاح کلمات نادرست دیگر گزینه</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها:</span></div><div><span class="az-text">۲‏) کوبید / ۳‏) قرار دادیم / ۴‏) مریض</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها را، بیمارها را</span></div></div>
                                        </div>', '<div id="2345331_view_1">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice1 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> اَنتُنَّ کَتَبتُنَّ دَرسَکُنَّ: شما درستان را نوشتید.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2345331_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> هِی طَرقَت بابَ غُرفَتها: او می</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">کوبد در خانه</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">اش را.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2345331_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> وَ جَعَلنا مِن الماءِ کُلَّ شَیٍٔ حَیٍّ: و از ‌آب هر چیز زنده</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">ای را قرار می</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">دهیم.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2345331_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> اَنتِ طَبیبَةٌ</span><span class="cz-text">، تَفحَصینَ المَرضی بِدِقَّةٍ</span><span class="cz-text">: تو پزشکی، مریض را به دقت معاینه می</span><span>‌</span><span class="cz-text">کنی.</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '1', '20', '100', 'test', '0', '2025-03-21 10:56:47', '2025-03-21 10:56:47');
INSERT INTO questions_temps (id, category_question_id, front, back, p1, p2, p3, p4, answer, percentage, count, type, isfree, created_at, updated_at) VALUES ('1037', '208', '<div class="fullWidth">
                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="rz-text">کدام فعل مناسب جای خالی است؟ </span><span>«</span><span class="rz-text">أیُّها الاَصدِقاء ....... اِلی الصَّفِ قَبل دَقیقتینِ.</span><span>»</span></div></div>
                                                    </div>', '<div class="QuestionContent p-r-15 rtl ng-hide" ng-show="q.ShowStyle==2 &amp;&amp; q.CurrentImage=='a' &amp;&amp; q.CString==''" aria-hidden="true">
                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۲‏ پاسخ صحیح است. أیُّها الأصدقاء = أنتم </span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7225-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x27F5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-53373" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-53374" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53375" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-53376" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-53377" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.218em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">⟵</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-7225"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>⟵</script></span><span class="az-text"> ذَهبتُم (شما دوستان رفتید.)</span></div></div>
