                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> اَنا مُدرِّسَةُ</span><span class="cz-text"> الکیمیاء اَشرحُ الدَّرس</span></div>
