                                                        </div>', '<div id="2353819_view_2">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> لِمَن یَحمِلُ الفَرس</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2353819_view_3">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice3 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> مَن یَحمِلُ الحَقیبَةَ</span></div>
                                                        </div>', '<div id="2353819_view_4">
                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice4 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> ماذا یَفعَلُ الفَرس</span></div>
