                                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.Choice2 | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><span class="cz-text"> مَنْ تِلْکَ الْمَرْأةُ</span><span class="cz-text">؟ ....... اُمُّ حَمیدٍ. (هِیَ)</span></div>
