                                            <p ng-bind-html="q.AnswerText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div><span class="az-text">گزینه ۳‏ پاسخ صحیح است. معنی جمله</span><span>‌</span><span class="az-text">ها:</span></div><div><span class="az-text">امین: ‌آیا در ژاپن شهرها و روستاهای بسیاری وجود دارد؟            احمد: بله، وجود دارد.</span></div><div><span class="az-text">(توضیح: (</span><span class="az-formula"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span id="MathJax-Element-7976-Frame" class="mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML" tabindex="0" data-mathml='&lt;math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"&gt;&lt;mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;mi&gt;there&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mpadded width="3px" /&gt;&lt;mi&gt;are&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mstyle&gt;&lt;/math&gt;' style="position: relative;" role="presentation"><span id="MJXc-Node-60091" class="mjx-math" aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-60092" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-60093" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-60094" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-60095" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.432em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">there</span></span><span id="MJXc-Node-60096" class="mjx-mpadded"><span class="mjx-block" style="width: 0px; margin-top: -1em; padding: 0px 0.214em 0px 0px;"><span class="mjx-box" style="width: 0px; margin: 0px;"><span id="MJXc-Node-60097" class="mjx-mrow"></span></span><span class="mjx-strut"></span></span></span><span id="MJXc-Node-60098" class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.146em; padding-bottom: 0.361em;">are</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>there</mi><mpadded width="3px"></mpadded><mi>are</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="mat