                                                        <p ng-bind-html="q.QuestionText | unsafe" class="ng-binding"></p><div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Hossein: How do you say O-O? Is it the same in all words?</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Shayan: No, it's sometimes different.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Hossein: ....... ?</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Shayan: Yes, that sound is short in 'football' and long in 'afternoon'.</span></div></div>
