aria-hidden="true"><span id="MJXc-Node-60399" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-60400" class="mjx-mstyle"><span id="MJXc-Node-60401" class="mjx-mrow"><span id="MJXc-Node-60402" class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.432em; padding-bottom: 0.289em; padding-right: 0.106em;">F</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>F</mi></mstyle></math></span></span><script type="math/mml" id="MathJax-Element-8021"><math display="inline" displaystyle="true"><mstyle displaystyle="true" dir="ltr"><mi>F</script></span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Shayan: Mr. Chaychi, this is my cousin Sam. He speaks.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">French, English, and a littel persian.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Teacher: Oh, nice to meet you, Sam.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Sam: Nice to meet you, too.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Teacher: Are you from Iran?</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Sam: Yes, I'm originally Iranian, but I live in France.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Teacher: Welcome to our class. How do you like it in Iran?</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">Sam: Iran is great! I love it. It's a beautiful country.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">1- Mr. Chaychi is a student.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">2- Sam is not good at speaking English.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">3- Shayan lives in France.</span></div><div class="rz-ltr "><span class="rz-entext">4- Sam likes Iran.</span></div></div>
